![](http://blog-img-1255388623.cossh.myqcloud.com/tilestrata-underzoom-original-20190708145711.png)

underzoom 放大两倍的效果：

![](http://blog-img-1255388623.cossh.myqcloud.com/tilestrata-underzoom-result-20190708145813.png)

